{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_51_02",
  "title": "鈴村優 2話 推しグッズで運試し",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――アンケート提出の翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day after submitting the questionnaire",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8050.000000000001,
          "startTime": 8.05
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "優と一緒に『オタ活』って一体何をするのかしら\n私でも出来ることなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder what exactly we'll be doing for \"otaku activities\" with Yu.\nIs it something I can do too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.2333333214
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "オタ活というのは自分の好きなものに\n熱中して行う活動……のようですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Otaku activities are about doing something\nyou like in passion… I guess…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.8351929546
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "二人とも安心してな！　今日から撮影日まで\nうちがしっかりみっちり『もんバケ』を布教するで～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't you worry‚ you two! From today until the shoot‚\nI'll make sure to thoroughly promote \"Monbake\"!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.8391607802
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふっふ～。徹夜で布教用の資料も作って来たんよ\nまずはそれを見ながらアニメ鑑賞会や！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fu fu fu~. I stayed up all night making materials for the promotion!\nFirst‚ let's have an anime watching party while we look over these!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.2945121964
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "重っ……凄い分厚さね。百ページくらいありそうだわ\n優の誕生日までにしっかり全部覚えないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's heavy… and so thick. It looks about a hundred pages.\nI'll have to memorize all of it before Yu's birthday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.9822698813,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.9278455298
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\n私も『もんバケ』が好きになれるように頑張りますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you!\nI'll do my best to come to love \"Monbake\" as well!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.3634239396
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "なんや、二人ともそんなに身構えんでええんよ\nうちは二人にも楽しんでもらいたいだけなんやから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You know‚ you two don't have to be so stiff.\nI just want you two to have fun‚ like I do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "ハマってくれたらもちろんそれは嬉しいけどな\n「好き」の強制はしたくないんや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ I'd be happy if you fell in love with it‚\nbut I don't want to force \"my love\" on you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.2868025344
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "うちは全力で布教させてもらう。でも、もし\n面白くなかったら正直に「面白くない」って言ってな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll promote with all my heart. But if you\nfind it boring‚ just honestly tell me it's \"boring‚\" okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.3288695645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.2088430604
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "オタクにとって……自分が布教した作品の感想は\nどんなものでも美味しいご馳走なんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For an otaku… hearing someone's thoughts on a work they promoted\nis like a delicious feast whatever it is!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "作品についての解釈は人それぞれ違う……だからこそ\n面白い！　二人とも、とことん語り合いましょ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone has a different interpretation of a work… and that's what makes it\ninteresting! Let's all talk about it thoroughly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.1024316456,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8887.293868899988,
          "startTime": 97.9897255145
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――\"Miracle☆Idol Birthday!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.6230573219,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "撮影当日in池袋",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Filming day in Ikebukuro",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.5497275289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.903061871
    },
    {
