      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 99
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.2
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.4286422916
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ～やっぱり池袋のアニメストアはええなぁ\nグッズ買うために開店前から並ぶのなんて久しぶりやわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa~ Ikebukuro's anime stores are still great~\nIt's been a while since I lined up before opening just to buy merch.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.554940975
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん、沙季ちゃん、スタッフさん達\n本日はどうぞよろしくお願いします～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan‚ Saki-chan‚ and everyone on staff‚\nplease take care of us today~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.7320159478
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "あの……今日の優ちゃんの髪形……もしかして\nペト君の妹、ロマーラちゃん意識してたりしますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… Yu-chan‚ your hairstyle today… is it perhaps…\n…inspired by Romara-chan‚ Peto-kun's little sister?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.4241198741
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "せやねん！　せっかくやからってヘアメイクさんが\nしてくれたんよ。よう気付いてくれたなぁ、嬉しいわ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right! My hair and makeup artist\ndid it for me. I'm so happy you noticed!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.0666620891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.5595393065
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "優ちゃんの布教のおかげで私も『もんバケ』オタクに\nなりましたから。今日は一緒に楽しみます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks to Yu's promotion‚ I've become a \"Monbake\" otaku\nmyself. So‚ let's have fun together today!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.7333287557,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.4052081629
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "沙季ちゃん……嬉し過ぎて涙が……うちなオタク仲間と\n一緒にオタ活するの……ほんまに夢やってん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saki-chan… I'm so happy I could cry… Doing otaku activities\nwith a fellow fan was truly a dream of mine…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.5999954224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.2403098309
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私だってちゃんと『もんバケ』オタクに\nなったわよ！　ところで、今日は私達、何をするの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-Hey‚ I've also become a \"Monbake\" otaku\nproperly! By the way‚ what are we doing today?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.9648599085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.1069764976
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_51_02-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "アニメショップで『もんバケ』のグッズを買って\nその後はコラボカフェに行って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're going to buy \"Monbake\" merch at the anime shop‚\nthen go to the collaboration cafe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.0999954224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 169.1270900294
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
